channel.title: Error Much?
channel.description:
I am new to this so please don't think I am a newb :P
Well, I was running MoparScape...and for some unknown reason....it exited out on me. What is wrong, It runs fine for a second, on wedclient and downloaded client...it says Downloading File and then it exits...I had it to 91% once and it happened. What can I do to stop that?

item.title: Error Much?
